text:
"The Coop" is in the COOLEST part of town -- about 3-4 blocks to Bouldin Creek Cafe (Vegeterian, with Nutella Mocha) and a few blocks to La Patisserie with French chocolates & caramels and People's Art.

Free wifi, large back yard with a chicken coop (no chix). A few blocks from buses 10 and Congress Ave. No pets.

Guests run the thermostat on main level while owners sleep upstairs.
title: Comfy Private Guest Room
